org.vadere.simulator.models.osm

Interface AgentOSM

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, DynamicElement, PointPositioned, ScenarioElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HorseOSM, PedestrianOSM

    public interface AgentOSM
extends DynamicElement
    Representation of an Agent inside of the OptimalStepsModel. Only classes implementing this Interface can be used with the OptimalStepsModel.
